\lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\ red and round. This is a praise in terms of a womans beauty, and our Sages explained the allegory to 
\lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\ mean: even your worthless ones (\lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\ ריקנים\lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\ , lit. empty ones) are full of mitzvoth as a pomegranate. \lang1033\ltrch\f2\fs36\b\i0\ul0\cf2\cb10\ from 
