\lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\ festive pilgrimages, O daughter of princes! \lang1033\ltrch\f2\fs36\b\i0\ul0\cf2\cb10\ The curves of your thighs are like jewels\lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\  A collection of 
