\lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\ round as a thigh. \lang1033\ltrch\f2\fs36\b\i0\ul0\cf2\cb10\ like jewels\lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\  Heb. \lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\ חלאים\lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\ , like the hollow of \lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\ (חולית)\lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\  a pit. \lang1033\ltrch\f2\fs36\b\i0\ul0\cf2\cb10\ the handiwork of a 
\lang1033\ltrch\f2\fs36\b\i0\ul0\cf2\cb10\ craftsman\lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\  [They are] the [work of the] hands of the Holy One, blessed be He. [See] Tractate Succah 
