\lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\ Him from top to bottom. They commence, so to speak, from His head is as finest gold, and 
\lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\ progressively descend to His legs are as pillars of marble, since they come to appease Him, to draw 
