\lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\ Hananiah, Mishael and Azariah, who were like breasts for you to suckle from. They were like clusters 
\lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\ [of dates], which shower liquid; so did they nurse lavishly and teach everyone that there is no fear like 
\lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\ fear of You. Until this point, the nations praise Him. From here on are the words of the Shechinah to 
